    <j.0:event_legal_type rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Position de la Commission sur les amendements du PE en première lecture</j.0:event_legal_type>
    <j.0:comment xml:lang="fr">Out of the 18 amendments adopted (1, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 14, 15, 16, 17, 18, 19, 20, and 21) , the Commission has accepted 13 (amendments 1, 3, 5, 6, 8, 9, 10, 11, 14, 15, 16, 17 and 21) in the form proposed by the Parliament. Three amendments (7, 19 and 20) were accepted in principle and the remaining two (2 and 18) were rejected.</j.0:comment>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/cdm#entity_temporal"/>
    <j.0:event_initiated_by_institution rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COM"/>
    <j.0:event_legal_comment xml:lang="fr">Out of the 18 amendments adopted (1, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 14, 15, 16, 17, 18, 19, 20, and 21) , the Commission has accepted 13 (amendments 1, 3, 5, 6, 8, 9, 10, 11, 14, 15, 16, 17 and 21) in the form proposed by the Parliament. Three amendments (7, 19 and 20) were accepted in principle and the remaining two (2 and 18) were rejected.</j.0:event_legal_comment>
    <j.0:uses rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/fd_602/1025"/>
  </rdf:Description>
